validator wired into `just validate-configs`, and write ADR-009 + doc updates. The durable learning
is a PLANNING learning: how to plan such a fix in this ecosystem AND, most importantly, the
catalogue of uncertain assumptions and unverified claims a reviewer must scrutinize before trusting
the plan. This lives in the canonical NATS topology skill so anyone searching "NATS leaf auth"
finds it next to the leaf.conf/server.conf port-7422 topology it already documents.

